Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.99,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're never sure, we never cure this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:39.33,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Can't get enough to end these ridiculous things
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.62,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're all praying for the time to change
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.37,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All facts sound like a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.42,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now whatcha gonna get from the present world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.38,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nothing should be left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.55,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But keep your eyes straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.09,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Break through the longest night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.72,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sharpen your mind and set your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.14,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Never doubt what you can do
Comment: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.94,IN JP,,0,0,0,,-------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.99,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们无法保证 也无法治愈这伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:39.33,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们也无法阻止这些荒谬的事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.62,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们皆祈祷变革到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.37,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管事实听起来如在梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.42,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你从这世界掌握到了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.38,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要留下遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.55,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持视线向前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.09,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撕裂漫漫长夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.72,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用你锋利的内心作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.14,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要怀疑自己的能力
